WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:05.280
It's a very gross thing.
You have to come to that subtler plane,

00:00:05.280 --> 00:00:11.920
otherwise you miss it. And some people can
never get it. That's it.

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:19.120
Because it is such a subtle thing,
very subtle. You can say that supposing we

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:26.160
have a cold, then we cannot get the
fragrance. Only with cold we cannot get

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:31.680
the fragrance. Supposing we have no eyes,
we can't see. Even they exist,

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:35.920
we cannot see. Leave alone and enjoy.
At least you should be able to see.

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:41.280
You cannot see it. So these things have
grown into us as human beings,

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:48.880
that we see beauty, we see aesthetics,
and we get fragrance, and we see

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:54.800
cleanliness. All these things we
appreciate, while animals don't.

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:59.440
So we have become, we think we have become
very subtle, but we have not.

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:00.400
Since we are gross.

00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:04.480
You see, unless and until you go to the
sukshma, it is the sukshma.

00:01:04.480 --> 00:01:10.480
This is the, what you call,
the subtle thing. And for that,

00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:14.320
one has to be very subtle,
you see, your attention has to be very

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:19.280
subtle. Like you can say a needle is
there, and if you have to put the thread

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:26.880
into it, you see, it's a very subtle job.
And the needle has to have a big hole,

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:31.031
first of all, which seldomly I find.
That the space is so little,

00:01:31.031 --> 00:01:34.960
you see, there's very little space between
two thoughts. Like a thought rises and

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:39.520
falls off, you see. And there are many
thoughts around it, bombarded from ego,

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:45.200
superego and all that. And you are faced
with that immediately. So this attention

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:48.960
goes from here to this thought,
that thought, like that you start moving.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:52.400
And this is in between, here,
down below you have to touch it.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:57.120
This is a very subtle thing.
So what happens, you have to slow down.

00:01:57.120 --> 00:02:02.000
And slow down to that limit that you stay
there. Moreover, this gap has to be

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:08.800
bigger. When you have to put the needle
into the thread, you have to slow down.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:14.840
You have to make the needle correct,
in the sense it should be put in a correct

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:24.000
way. And the thread is to be nicely,
you see, put right. And it is subtle.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:29.200
But those who have never done it,
cannot do it. It is the depthness also one

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:34.160
has to develop. It is the depthness one
has to develop.

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:40.000
Now with Sahaja Yoga, it is something so
wonderful, which I do not know if you have

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:44.320
noticed or not. It's such a wonderful
thing, that you have had no craving as

00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:50.480
such a Kundalini like. You have developed
no depthness about it. You have had no

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:55.680
sort of experience of the sukshma before
it. But as soon as you get it,

00:02:55.680 --> 00:03:02.240
the whole thing comes to you in a parcel.
You can raise the kundalini,

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:06.480
you can give them realization,
you can feel the collective consciousness.

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:13.440
Immediately you start feeling.
But the gross part is around.

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:15.120
So one has to be very careful.

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:20.000
Now a person who is sort of possessed,
for such a person he is even more

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.720
difficult. Because, you see,
when he is possessed, all his gaps are

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:28.080
already filled in, with the possession.
So he can never find that subtle thing,

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:32.640
because he has a barrier already around
him. First of all he should be free.

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:36.640
All the possessions have to go away.
But, you see, by so many things we are

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:46.000
possessed. We are so much possessed by
ideas, which we think are very great,

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:51.840
you see. Something, like some people think
that money is something great,

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:57.440
or some power is very great.
And sometimes we find them so hopelessly

00:03:57.440 --> 00:04:02.880
gross. And they talk of very gross things.
I mean, so mundane and so gross,

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:05.920
that you don't know what to do with your
Sahaja Yoga. I mean, you don't know how to

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:09.840
put the needle, you see,
because all the needles don't have whole

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:15.120
eye, because they are filled with lot of
mud, which is to be cleansed,

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:17.680
and cleaned and put away.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:25.280
While cleaning something naturally it
hurts. That's why the people get hurt.

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:28.480
The reason why in Sahaja Yoga,
I've seen, always it happens.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:32.800
Lots of people will come in the beginning.
Then gradually they go on reducing.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:36.880
Because it hurts them. You see,
first getting Realization is all right.

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:41.040
But then it comes back to the cleaning
part. In that cleaning you have to do the

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:45.120
cleaning. Then you hurt yourself.
It is very difficult to clean yourself

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:49.840
something, because others are doing well
and good. But you are not under the

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:53.360
masses. You are quite aware.
And you have to do cleaning also.

00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:58.800
So for that you have to do little bit of
exercise in the sense that you have to sit

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:05.600
before the photograph, cleanse yourself,
little bit of listen also.

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:10.800
Now listening is, you know that I'm not
like other gurus, that I give you left and

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:18.080
right, sort of orders like that.
Nor do I go to a large extent in imposing

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:22.240
anything. I give you your freedom
and your wisdom to decide.

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:28.000
But still, you have to see My mood very
important, you see, because this mood is

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:33.920
not rational or I have not brought it
deliberately. It comes to Me because it

00:05:33.920 --> 00:05:35.360
means something.

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:38.560
So I'll give an example.
A Gregor's uncle was coming here.

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:44.000
He asked Me first, Mother,
should I have him for the ashram?

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:49.120
Now I was swinging little bit here
and there, you see. But he didn't

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:52.320
understand that I was trying to sort of
pass it over. Then he said,

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:55.440
there is no hotel available.
Because the fellow said,

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:59.680
I'm coming in a week. I'm coming four days
earlier. Now this is all satanic.

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:03.840
This is all satanic force that is building
up. They know ashram is here.

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:08.760
So make him go four days earlier,
give ideas. So he comes here four days

00:06:08.760 --> 00:06:13.520
earlier. Now you being a good man,
you think that how can you say no to him?

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:17.440
But at this time you should say that,
you see, you are coming here but I,

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:22.320
this ashram, I'm just staying here myself.
And so I can, nobody can come

00:06:22.320 --> 00:06:25.680
and stay here till they are sahaja yogis.
And we cannot have you around,

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:29.520
we are sorry. But you can wait
and I'll find out some place for you.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:37.520
But I cannot have things according to your
program. And when you say this,

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:41.440
then immediately even the possession will
leave that person. Because he is just

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:46.480
there to spoil our work here.
And that's how many a times it has

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:51.200
happened. One David came
and you were all having some assaults

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:56.720
and you were all going round
and round and round. But that,

00:06:56.720 --> 00:07:00.000
it so happened that, you see,
it was just brought to me that it should

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:03.680
be so and he should be there
and all these things. So I didn't know

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:08.480
what to do, you see. Of course I can play
little tricks so that they are not there.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:10.560
So I played a trick on him
and he went away.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:15.440
But to begin with only, don't try to bring
things to your problems,

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:20.560
you see. Already you are here like a
hospital, are getting yourself treated.

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:26.080
So don't have horrible people by which you
get more wounded. This is what I am trying

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:29.520
to tell you. But sometimes you know people
feel hurt, they don't like it.

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:33.040
Small things small thing they feel hurt
with the problem, you see.

00:07:33.040 --> 00:07:38.160
And it's very difficult to explain to
people, to understand. There is nothing to

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:43.520
get angry. After all, this is a very
subtle thing. You are working out

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:47.520
something subtle and there should be no
more disturbance. Because again the gross

00:07:47.520 --> 00:07:51.680
disturbance is coming. Then again you have
to fight it. What's the use?

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:56.240
You see, it is like a complete penance,
a tapasya as they call it.

00:07:56.240 --> 00:08:00.960
It's a penance. So that you have to
dedicate your complete attention to it

00:08:00.960 --> 00:08:06.640
and you have to be in the subtle condition
and you must then establish yourself

00:08:06.640 --> 00:08:06.960
fully.

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:11.200
Once you have fully established,
then you'll be amazed that no badha will

00:08:11.200 --> 00:08:13.600
touch you. On the contrary,
wherever you'll walk, the badhas will be

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:19.040
going away. In Rahuri we have three very
strong people, only three of them.

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:23.520
And they go on a motorbike in the night
somewhere or something. They go at about

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:29.680
twelve o'clock, they go any time they feel
like. So some of the spirits,

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:33.200
you see, came in the dreams of some of the
people and told them that,

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:37.920
tell them to go at least one by one,
not three of them together,

00:08:37.920 --> 00:08:42.240
otherwise we'll be completely finished.
See, they came and told like this.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.120
And then people came and told them that,
please, you know, they came

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:48.960
and told us something in the dreams that
you go with three of them together,

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:52.160
otherwise they'll be all finished.
So many things happen like that,

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:52.880
you see.

00:08:52.880 --> 00:08:58.320
So when you become very subtle person,
if you carry a little of,

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:04.480
say, my kumkum in your finger or
something, and they understand you so

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:11.120
well. Some people went some place in a
village and so some people came

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:16.160
and they said, they were all sort of
spiritualist type. They said,

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:21.200
let's see now what is your Sahaja Yoga,
let's see this challenge.

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:25.920
They said, let us see how we work it out,
your Sahaja Yoga. So they said,

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:32.320
all right, you sit down.
And they said, try to cure this man or

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:39.040
something. So they put the hand on that
person. So he said, what is this?

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:42.960
You, it is Mataji curing me or you are
curing? Again he would feel their hands,

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:46.560
open his eyes. He said, how?
He said, I can hear them.

00:09:48.080 --> 00:09:52.960
And I can feel it. And you are wearing her
kada (metal bracelet ideally) in the hand

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:57.600
and you are doing in her name,
is it? Like that you will talk to them.

00:09:57.600 --> 00:10:00.560
And they have recorded all this.
So this kind of thing can happen.

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:05.120
You see, they talk. These negative people,
they talk and they tell you.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:09.200
And they talk quite, I mean,
it is quite audible. People can record it

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:12.400
now that maybe was saying,
I have recorded it. It's very easy to

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:15.920
record all these voices.
Sometimes these voices come through human

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:19.920
beings or sometimes from the air you can
hear such voices coming and all kinds of

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:21.920
things they say.

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:27.200
But to be subtle, you see,
is to be in the present.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:32.080
In the past, if you go, or in the future,
if you go, then you cannot be subtle.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:37.120
Subtle means to be in the present.
So that is the way you are going to be in

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:41.280
the subtle part of yourself.
If you think about the future or the past,

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:46.400
then it is not the subtle position.
To subtle yourself, to make your subtler

00:10:46.400 --> 00:10:51.440
and subtler, you should be in the present.
Now as I told you about the needle,

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:56.080
now the needle is like that,
straight. And the hand is going like this.

00:10:56.080 --> 00:11:04.160
Now if the needle is here or here,
then it can't go. So the Kundalini has to

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:07.760
pass through the chakras.
The chakras should be absolutely placed in

00:11:07.760 --> 00:11:11.600
the centre. They should not be this side
pulled or that side. If they are,

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:15.840
then the Kundalini doesn't know how to get
in. And then that's how you get pain in

00:11:15.840 --> 00:11:19.680
your chakras or the Kundalini goes
and sort of bangs, you see,

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:24.960
at the closed side. And that's how you see
the whole thing, pulsation and is going.

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:28.800
Then the Kundalini spreads on all the
sides. You see it moving on this side

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:36.347
and making some, sort of a pulsation
there. You see all those movements and all

00:11:36.347 --> 00:11:42.000
that. So to be subtle means to be in the
present. Just to come in the present,

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:47.200
neither in the past nor post.
And when you are there, you'll be amazed

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:52.400
that Kundalini will be straight up like
that. Just like this straight up.

00:11:52.400 --> 00:11:58.640
But people are in the present for a very
short time. Because as I told you,

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:03.040
the present is just a little bit.
But if you can increase the space,

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.560
then it can be.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:09.520
Now for this increase of the space,
you must meditate. If you do not meditate,

00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:12.640
this space will remain like this.
And at the slightest pretext,

00:12:12.640 --> 00:12:16.000
you'll be catching. At the slightest
pretext, you'll be in trouble.

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:20.480
So meditation is the way you can do it.
Now what is meditation? How to do it?

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:24.720
It's first to sit down and watch your
thoughts to begin with. When you watch

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:28.640
your thoughts, you'll find there are still
thoughts coming and thoughts coming.

00:12:28.640 --> 00:12:33.680
Then you can ask your mind,
now let me see what are you thinking.

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:36.560
Still the mind is thinking.
You can do one more thing.

00:12:36.560 --> 00:12:44.560
It's to breathe in and breathe out.
Thrice you can do that. Deep breathing and

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:50.720
breathing out. After that,
you do three breathings in which you try

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:56.640
to bring breathing to a very low degree.
In the third one, I mean this is the first

00:12:56.640 --> 00:13:02.480
phase, then the second. In the third one
you breathe in such a manner that

00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:08.320
breathing becomes absolutely equal to
zero. You'll be amazed with this kind of a

00:13:08.320 --> 00:13:12.551
breathing thing. What happens with the
breathing? The thoughts,

00:13:12.551 --> 00:13:15.200
you see, move with that.
But when you bring it to the zero,

00:13:15.200 --> 00:13:20.400
it means you are in the present.
So that is how also you work out.

00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:23.440
But this is a sort of a,
we can say, an exercise.

00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:27.360
But this is only possible after
realization because after realization your

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:31.040
kundalini is activated and it has a
meaning. But if you do before realization,

00:13:31.040 --> 00:13:35.920
it will be going wrong. Before
realization, if you do any one of these

00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:39.920
things, you will be absolutely on the
other side. It is something so funny.

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:44.720
But it happens even in practical life that
if you try to do something,

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:48.160
like you want to start a car
and there's no key on and you go on

00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:53.280
jamming it, the car will never start.
On the contrary, the car will be spoilt.

00:13:53.280 --> 00:13:56.560
But when the car is opened up,
then if you put the brakes

00:13:56.560 --> 00:14:02.000
or you raise the accelerator,
you can do it. But when car is not started

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:04.560
and then you start doing it,
the car will be spoiled.

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:07.120
There will be no movement.
On the contrary, the car will move

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:11.600
backwards at the most. It will never move
forward. It will not be in your control.

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:17.440
And this is what is tantrism.
This is what tantrism is,

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:24.320
and the tantrikas, which is so called the
usage of tantrism; actually tantrikas are

00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:28.880
really sahaja yogis because they know how
to use the tantra that is Kundalini.

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:32.080
But these (false tantrikas) are the
horrible people who are not realized

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:36.000
and they are trying to play with it.
And by doing that, what they are doing,

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:41.680
are creating a sort of a barrier after
barrier by which they are spoiling the

00:14:41.680 --> 00:14:46.080
tantra and they are going in the other
direction. And the movement in the

00:14:46.080 --> 00:14:51.440
backward direction, they call it as a
movement in the upward direction.

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:56.320
So it's just in opposition of real tantra,
you see.

00:14:56.320 --> 00:15:00.800
All the spiritual world should be under
this. All the spiritual healers

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:04.880
and all kinds of spiritual healers must be
brought under this category.

00:15:04.880 --> 00:15:08.800
Though here they are called as spiritual
healers, but tantrikas, because they have

00:15:08.800 --> 00:15:13.680
gone against the tantra by which they have
spoiled the tantra. They have spoiled the

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:16.800
tantra and by spoiling it,
whatever comes out of it,

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:21.600
they think this is something like a fruit,
you see. Now you can putrefy a fruit.

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:26.720
If you putrefy the fruit,
it can become into a wine.

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:30.320
Then you say, oh, this is a wonderful
thing. It is like that. This is the

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:33.840
putrefaction of your being,
which gives you these odors

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:38.160
and things and that you start thinking,
oh, this is wine, very good.

00:15:38.160 --> 00:15:41.280
And so, in the beginning,
you know, no one likes these things.

00:15:41.280 --> 00:15:43.680
For example, whiskey, people say,
is very difficult to take in the

00:15:43.680 --> 00:15:48.320
beginning. But gradually it so works out,
gradually, that you develop a taste for

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:54.240
it. You can start developing a taste for
anything. If you work it you can.

00:15:54.240 --> 00:15:58.320
So this is what happens,
is in a subtle thing it can become

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:04.320
absolutely gross. The whole thing is
ruined and absolutely finished.

00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:09.600
So because of these possessions,
all these gurus are nothing but tantrikas.

00:16:09.600 --> 00:16:13.520
All of them are tantrikas.
Nothing but tantrikas. They are within

00:16:13.520 --> 00:16:19.360
spirits. Now how do they get into spirits?
How do they master the spirits?

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:22.240
How are they there? Like,
as I was saying, let us take the analogy

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:28.160
of the car. Car has to go forward,
upward on a thing. All right?

00:16:28.160 --> 00:16:34.800
You have come all the way upto human
stage. Now, the car has not yet started.

00:16:34.800 --> 00:16:37.440
You cannot control the car.
You cannot raise it higher.

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:43.040
So it goes on. What do you do?
If you leave the brake, it goes on.

00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:46.400
You put the accelerator,
doesn't work out. If you put the

00:16:46.400 --> 00:16:50.080
accelerator, it may accelerate,
you are going down. So you go down.

00:16:50.080 --> 00:16:54.720
This movement starts. Now you go into any
khat, you don't know which side you will

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:58.560
fall. You see, they fall into this side
and that side. First they get hurt,

00:16:58.560 --> 00:17:03.200
again they get into the car.
Again they start, again they go this side,

00:17:03.200 --> 00:17:06.560
that side, God knows whether they go to
the left or to the right.

00:17:06.560 --> 00:17:10.720
Sometimes they also get into a mixed
condition. So whichever way,

00:17:10.720 --> 00:17:15.920
wherever they go, whatever side they fall,
they meet all these horrible people.

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:18.640
They say, oh, doesn't matter.
You see, we look after you,

00:17:18.640 --> 00:17:22.960
we will help you. And they put them down,
and more and more. And we will give you

00:17:22.960 --> 00:17:27.440
powers. Now what are the powers of
quality? These are the powers how to fall

00:17:27.440 --> 00:17:33.280
fast. And there is no parachuting,
but it's really falling down.

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:40.000
And they have no idea as to how you fall
down. They just fall as,

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:45.760
just like somebody is thrown from a place,
just like that. But they think it is a

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:50.880
force (power). They do not understand the
ascent. They think this is a force

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:56.560
(power). And they call it as Kundalini
awakening. What do you say to such people.

00:17:56.560 --> 00:18:03.040
And that's how the whole set of Kundalini,
is spoilt. The complete concept is spoilt

00:18:03.040 --> 00:18:06.560
to such an extent that they have spoilt
all our scriptures, they have spoilt

00:18:06.560 --> 00:18:11.840
everything. Because these people became,
you see, a great conscience keeper of all

00:18:11.840 --> 00:18:19.920
the horrible things we have.
So they used to give them a very good

00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:30.800
support for their fall, you see.
And they confused God with this fall.

00:18:30.800 --> 00:18:35.440
This confusion was done by tantrika.
And this is why, yesterday I was talking

00:18:35.440 --> 00:18:41.440
to Gregor and there, and you see,
someone gave an idea that,

00:18:41.440 --> 00:18:47.600
you see, first the God was separated,
and sex was separated. It was not

00:18:47.600 --> 00:18:51.840
confused, even in England and all that.
But then these gurus came in,

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:54.800
and these tantrikas came in,
and these things came in,

00:18:54.800 --> 00:18:58.960
and then they gave the idea.
But I say Freud also. Freud is another

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:04.240
great tantrika. These are another horrible
thing. So they gave these ideas.

00:19:04.240 --> 00:19:09.680
With these ideas all the subtle was
covered, and man became absolutely,

00:19:09.680 --> 00:19:18.320
what you call, the lame thing of these
tantrikas. And there are ways

00:19:18.320 --> 00:19:20.240
and means how they work it out.

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:23.920
So to come to Sahaja Yoga,
one has to know that you have to be very,

00:19:23.920 --> 00:19:30.160
very sort of surrendering about it.
Because if you come to Sahaja Yoga,

00:19:30.160 --> 00:19:34.880
you say, all right, I will see about it.
If it works, I'll accept it.

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:39.040
Sahaja Yoga is not going to fall at your
feet. You have to accept,

00:19:39.040 --> 00:19:41.920
because this is a subtle thing.
You see, something gross,

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:45.280
it's very easy to pick up.
But this is subtle, so you have to seek

00:19:45.280 --> 00:19:50.320
the subtle. Like a needle would say,
a needle and thread is there.

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:56.000
And if somebody says, I will see if the
needle gets the thread in,

00:19:56.000 --> 00:20:01.760
I will go to it, otherwise I won't.
No. That is not possible.

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:05.920
You see, whatever you may say,
it cannot be done. Like other gurus are

00:20:05.920 --> 00:20:11.360
doing, I cannot do it. You have to cleanse
your holes and you have to put the thing

00:20:11.360 --> 00:20:16.640
properly, with proper concentration and
surrender. Otherwise it will not work.

00:20:16.640 --> 00:20:21.360
So this is why in Sahaja Yoga the
surrendering is not the way the other

00:20:21.360 --> 00:20:24.880
gurus want of money or sort of bending
before them and all that.

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:29.200
That is not the thing that is wanted.
From the heart you must know that you have

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:34.240
to come to a point where you are in the
present. So you cut out your ego,

00:20:34.240 --> 00:20:36.800
you cut out your superego
and you be in the present.

00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:40.640
This is what is surrendering
and this is wisdom.

00:20:40.640 --> 00:20:45.760
If you just say that, why not Mataji
should give us an instant thing.

00:20:45.760 --> 00:20:50.560
I mean, you cannot demand anything from
Me. You cannot. I mean, this is not your

00:20:50.560 --> 00:20:55.440
right, demand. But, I mean,
I am working it out, I am trying,

00:20:55.440 --> 00:21:02.240
my hard. But you have to come to one point
that this is very subtle stuff,

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:07.840
extremely subtle. And even the slightest
thing can spoil it. That's why there is a

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:13.520
protocol about it. You see,
everything is to be weighed very carefully

00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:19.040
and see. And gradually the things start
flowering and then you find beautiful

00:21:19.040 --> 00:21:26.640
flowers. But in the beginning it's a very
big dynamic change, very dynamic method by

00:21:26.640 --> 00:21:31.120
which the whole thing works out
and very delicate too. So keeping all the

00:21:31.120 --> 00:21:35.680
delicacies and everything intact is only
possible if you try to keep in the

00:21:35.680 --> 00:21:40.720
present. And forget what has happened in
the past and forget what you are going to

00:21:40.720 --> 00:21:44.720
have in the future. Actually still the
past is lingering on your minds.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:49.440
It makes your heart and chakra very weak.
Your all left side is very weak in that.

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:52.720
Now if you think of the future,
then your right side is very weak.

00:21:52.720 --> 00:21:57.200
Now what am I to do? I want you to be in
the center. And once you are in the center

00:21:57.200 --> 00:22:02.080
you will achieve both of them.
You can achieve both the things very well

00:22:02.080 --> 00:22:07.520
because the wisdom balances all that.
So that you will be able to balance your

00:22:07.520 --> 00:22:12.320
heart and your being. Absolutely.
A complete integration takes place.

00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:18.615
So everything comes out and you never lose
and you feel very happy about it.

00:22:18.615 --> 00:22:18.640
And it can be remarkable.

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:23.360
So it's a very subtle thing
and should not be disturbing to anyone if

00:22:23.360 --> 00:22:27.120
somebody you find is gross.
He is gross, all right. She is gross,

00:22:27.120 --> 00:22:31.280
all right. We are not there.
We are here at the end. At the most we can

00:22:31.280 --> 00:22:34.800
tell her that, see, this is very subtle.
If you want to achieve it,

00:22:34.800 --> 00:22:38.560
you have to be subtle. So now give up all
these gross things. Otherwise this won't

00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:42.480
work out. I was also of your type.
Then, you know, if he wants to accept,

00:22:42.480 --> 00:22:45.920
he will accept. But there are so many
ways, you know, we can go on,

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:49.840
you see, beating out his gross things
and we can sort of taking out all that.

00:22:49.840 --> 00:22:55.280
We have so many ways of doing it.
But still, best thing is that we should

00:22:55.280 --> 00:23:01.120
wholeheartedly ask for it.
And once we ask for it wholeheartedly,

00:23:01.120 --> 00:23:11.274
it works out. It works out beautifully.
All right? Any questions?

